formula.name: Single KPI
formula.text:
SUM(CASE WHEN EKKO.BSART = 'ZP4T' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)
/
COUNT_TABLE("EKKO")

COUNT(
DISTINCT 
CASE 
WHEN "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN" = 'Change Quantity' AND "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."USER_TYPE" NOT IN (<%=automatic_users%>) THEN EKPO.MANDT || EKPO.EBELN || EKPO.EBELP ELSE NULL END)

meta.expressionLhs: ROUND_MONTH ( PU_FIRST ( "EKPO" , "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME" , "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN" = 'Create Purchase Order Item' ) ) AS "#{Round_Month}(#{_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES.EVENTTIME})" FORMAT "%Y-%m"
ROUND_MONTH ( PU_FIRST ( "AP_BSEG" , "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME" , "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_DE" = 'Erfasse im SAP' ) ) AS "#{Round_Month}(#{_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES.EVENTTIME})" FORMAT "%Y-%m"

formula.name: Single KPI
formula.text: KPI("Ratio",  PROCESS EQUALS 'Lieferant erstellt Rechnung' TO ANY TO 'Lege Bestellung an (Kopf)')

sheetFilter.text: --FILTER DOMAIN "EKPO"."BUKRS" || '-' || "EKPO"."BUKRS_TEXT" AS "#{\"EKPO\".\"BUKRS\"}" NOT IN ( '0040-Dieckerhoff Guss GmbH', '0036-Walter Hundhausen GmbH', '5010-FWH EG GMBH', '0167-FWH GmbH', '5050-FWH SG GMBH' );
